INTRIGUE—THE NEW NIGHTCLUB AT WYNN

The allure of Intrigue, at Wynn, promises to utterly captivate your senses. Intrigue offers 14,000 square-feet of stunning interiors and high energy excitement bathed in state-of-the-art light and sound. Step out onto the patio to enjoy an up-close vantage of the breathtaking waterfall and pyrotechnics. Experience performances by Cedric Gervais, Laidback Luke, Chuckie and other special guests. Every corner of the nightclub offers an opportunity to entice and surprise you, and every table offers the tone of a VIP experience. Satisfy your curiosity and you are sure to experience a night you won’t soon forget.

Resort guests receive preferred entry by purchasing tickets through the concierge at (702) 770-7070.


Open Thursday through Saturday at 10 p.m.
